description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions


Kate and Leisha discuss the new Beetles Documentary and vacationing in a snowy place. They then answer your questions about going on a bad date, their favorite vintage things, age gap relationships, reveling yourself to others, and emotional cheating.
